bio:
Lielle lives in Markarth, where she works as a servant at Understone Keep. Understone Keep is an ancient Dwemer keep built into the mountainside, used as a palace by the jarl of Markarth. From Understone Keep, the jarl rules over Markarth and the rest of The Reach (of which Markarth is the capital).
Lielle is a young petite Breton woman with light blonde hair and striking blue eyes, She usually wears a somewhat revealing barmaid outfit. She spends most of her working hours serving food and drinks to the inhabitants of the keep, as well as to important visitors.
Quotes:
"What can I do for you?"
"Need something?"
name: Lielle
